<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Feature Announcement</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 32px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content h2 { color: #333333; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .content p { color: #666666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; }
        .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
        .feature-highlight { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffecd2 0%, #fcb69f 100%); padding: 30px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; }
        .benefit-item { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; }
        .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #999999; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer a { color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ‰ <%= title || 'New Feature Unlocked!' %></h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hey <%= name %>,</h2>
            
            <p>We're excited to announce a powerful new feature that will take your LinkedIn game to the next level!</p>
            
            <div class="feature-highlight">
                <h3 style="color: #d84315; font-size: 28px; margin: 0;"><%= title || 'Amazing New Feature' %></h3>
                <p style="color: #555; font-size: 18px; margin: 15px 0 0 0;"><%= description || 'Discover what\'s new and how it helps you' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>What makes this special:</strong></p>
            
            <% if (typeof benefits !== 'undefined' && Array.isArray(benefits)) { %>
                <% benefits.forEach(function(benefit) { %>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <strong style="color: #333;"><%= benefit.title %></strong>
                        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;"><%= benefit.description %></p>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <strong style="color: #333;">âš¡ Faster & Smarter</strong>
                    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Enhanced performance for better results</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <strong style="color: #333;">ðŸŽ¯ More Accurate</strong>
                    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Improved AI for higher quality output</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <strong style="color: #333;">ðŸ’Ž Easy to Use</strong>
                    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Intuitive interface that just works</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:3000' %>/dashboard" class="cta-button">
                    Try It Now â†’
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #e8f5e9; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #2e7d32;">ðŸ’¡ Pro Tip:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #2e7d32;"><%= proTip || 'Combine this new feature with your existing workflow for maximum impact!' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <% if (typeof videoUrl !== 'undefined' && videoUrl) { %>
            <p style="text-align: center;"><strong>ðŸ“¹ Watch a quick tutorial:</strong><br>
            <a href="<%= videoUrl %>" style="color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;">Click here to learn more â†’</a></p>
            <% } %>
            
            <p><strong>We'd love your feedback!</strong> Try out the new feature and reply to this email to let us know what you think.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Keep innovating,<br><strong>The LinkedInPulse Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> LinkedInPulse. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> | 
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

